<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上在学校，大家都在谈论龙卷风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风正好经过柳树溪上方！”卡洛斯喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常棒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂，卡洛斯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂想了一下，说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们不应该喜欢龙卷风。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我喜欢。”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我说说你们家的龙卷风安全小组。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都提前计划好了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂是我们的组长。”乔伊说，对着凯蒂笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家一起合作。”凯蒂补充道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈和我做了急救箱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但幸运的是，我们没用上。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊在风暴过后找到了杰利！”凯蒂宣布道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，爸爸和我找到的。”乔伊害羞地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我家没有避难所。”卡洛斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，我们决定走廊是最安全的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为那里没有窗户。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风来时，玻璃碎片会很危险。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你家怎么样，卢克？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他忘了制定计划。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克不高兴地看了一眼她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在咖啡店听到的龙卷风警报。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈给每个人一个免费的脆皮派，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把他们带到了地下室。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爸爸亲眼看到了龙卷风。”拉里说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都去了暴风雨避难所。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但就在我爸爸关门之前，他抬头看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风正穿过田野！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们的谷仓升上天空，然后重重地摔了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它破成了碎片。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谷仓里有牛吗？”卡洛斯问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”拉里说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有我的自行车。我们还没有找到它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拉里，你说你的谷仓被毁了，我很难过。”希金斯老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>全班同学点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。”拉里说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的邻居今天过来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们会帮我爸爸建一个新谷仓。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们一起合作时，会非常有帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，希金斯老师问拉里龙卷风的声音听起来像什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拉里想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听起来像......就像一个......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“像火车！”凯蒂说，“轰轰！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它甚至像火车一样鸣笛！”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呜呜！ ”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得听起来像喷气式飞机。”卡洛斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“轰隆！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它发出了响声。”劳拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像我们把窗打开，然后车开得飞快。嗖！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像一只野生动物......一头狮子！”卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都开始发出可怕的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“逃生！”凯蒂大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的话把大家都逗笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，希金斯老师挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请安静！”他大喊道，“安静！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们听到敲门声，奥尔森校长走进教室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着希金斯老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从走廊走来时，好像听见了龙卷风声。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家又都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥尔森校长也笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希金斯老师。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“学校院子里满是在暴风雨中被吹倒的树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们班愿意帮忙打扫操场吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的！”所有学生都大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要帮忙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，课间休息的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希金斯老师把全班同学带到了操场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把所有的树枝堆成一大堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希金斯老师搬着沉重的树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉帮乔伊搬着一根大树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯找到一只蓝色运动鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂在滑梯下发现一把破伞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，孩子们站在他们的“树枝堆”前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥尔森校长拍了一张照片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，她把照片钉在走廊的布告板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在照片下面，她用大头针固定了几个大字：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>团队合作愉快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>